"text": "《职场诳人》EP 01：离婚律师 vs 婚姻咨询师正在热播。节目中，嘉宾们提到了「离婚力」。「离婚力」指个人在离婚时具备的能力，一般包括经济能力、精神独立的能力、意志坚定的能力等。女性在结婚前，是否要考虑自己是否具备「离婚力」？不具备「离婚力」就无法离婚吗？你如何看待「离婚力」？EP01：出轨还分等级吗？｜婚姻咨询师 vs 离婚律师"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-b71639aec937fe58d4b273ecc9d2225f_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "3.6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/627613420"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIkPO6pPq2nrFCEAMaCTEwMTc0ODQ5MiCoz96pBjAAOLgBQDByCTYyNzYxMzQyMHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "49_1699494152.24997", "card_id": "Q_621598937", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 201}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如果外面下雨，孩子执意要出门，你会同意吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-9df2756024a24f02519af289f5d3b244_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "3.6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/621598937"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIkPO6pPq2nrFCEAMaCTEwMDQxMjcyNCCokP6nBjAAONQBQDFyCTYyMTU5ODkzN3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}], "paging": {"is_end": true, "is_start": false, "next": "", "previous": "", "totals": 0}, "fresh_text": "热榜已更新", "display_num": 15, "display_first": true, "fb_bill_main_rise": 0, "head_zone": {"type": "billboard_lantern", "data": [{"id": "1701723544818515968", "link_url": "https://www.zhihu.com/org/pi-yao-qian-xian", "title": "辟谣专区", "source_type": 0, "attached_info": "Ci4QABoTMTcwMTcyMzU0NDgxODUxNTk2OHITMTcwMTcyMzU0NDgxODUxNTk2OHgA", "tag": "辟谣", "tag_bg_color": "GRD01A"}]}}